        public void setDeltaTmax(int newDeltaTmax)
        Allows for a new value of deltaTmax. This variable defaults to 1/3 of numBlocks. deltaTmax is the largest difference in block number for which the Mean Squared Displacement will be calculated.
        Parameters:
        newDeltaTmax - - The new value of deltaTmax.
